channel.title: RSPS Citellum Error
channel.description:
So I have downloaded Citellum, and am trying to get the server to work properly but when ran it gives this error:
[code][Launcher] Running Server... Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 19 at com.rs.utils.Utils.getItemDefinitionsSize(Utils.java:319) at com.rs.cache.loader.ItemsEquipIds.init(ItemsEquipIds.java:13)[ at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:61) press any key to continue...[/code]
Does anyone know the fix? If anyone can help please let me know.
